title: The Romantics - Rhythm Romance [1985]
description:
Most people remember The Romantics by the smash hit "Talking in Your Sleep". This is their 1985 album and a fun one. Mystified and Test of Time are my favorites.



The Romantics Formed 1977, Detroit, MI, United States 
Members Wally Palmar (vocals, guitar), Jimmy Marinos (drums, vocals, 1977-84, 1996-97), Mike Skill (guitar, 1977-81), Rich Cole (bass), Dave Petratos (drums, 1985-87), Coz Canler (guitar, 1981-present)
